name: "neonizado"
description:
Ricardus
Ricardus is the fusion between Ricardo Fort & Frida Kahlo, each edition can also have a shout out to other iconic celebrities.
everyone is waiting for what Ricardus will wear on Halloween, so he wants to try as much as possible before deciding. it seems that there were some neon clothes left after the drop and he grabbed them to look like a real Neonz, they may be unique but he is the most classy.
